-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#Intern\" title=\"Intern\">Intern<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#Chief_Executive_Officer\" title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">Chief Executive Officer<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#President\" title=\"President\">President<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#Director\" title=\"Director\">Director<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#Car_Collection\" title=\"Car Collection\">Car Collection<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ruchir Kumar Modi <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_111594_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_111594_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/ruchirmodi\/details\/experience\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Ruchir L Modi &#8211; LinkedIn<\/a><\/span><\/span> was born on Friday, 9 September 1994 (<strong>age 28 years; as of 2022<\/strong>) in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. His zodiac sign is Virgo. Ruchir attended the American School of Bombay (1997-2010) and the American School in London (2010-2012). He holds a bachelor&#8217;s degree in global business management from Regent&#8217;s University, London. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_111594_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_111594_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/ruchirmodi\/details\/experience\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Ruchir L Modi &#8211; LinkedIn<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111678\" style=\"width: 407px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-with-his-family.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111678\" class=\"wp-image-111678 \" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-with-his-family.jpg\" alt=\"Childhood picture of Ruchir Modi with his sister, mother, and father\" width=\"397\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-with-his-family.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-with-his-family-300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111678\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Childhood picture of Ruchir Modi with his sister, mother, and father<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 7&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Weight (approx.):<\/strong> 65 kg<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi..jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-111679\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi..jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi.\" width=\"353\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi..jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi.-238x300.jpg 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ruchir&#8217;s father&#8217;s name is <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/lalit-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Lalit Modi<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111680\" style=\"width: 448px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-father-Lalit-Modi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111680\" class=\" wp-image-111680\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-father-Lalit-Modi.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi with his father Lalit Modi\" width=\"438\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-father-Lalit-Modi.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-father-Lalit-Modi-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-father-Lalit-Modi-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi with his father Lalit Modi<\/p><\/div>\n<p>His mother&#8217;s name is <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/minal-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Minal Modi<\/a>. She passed away in 2018 after battling cancer.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111697\" style=\"width: 347px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111697\" class=\" wp-image-111697\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Childhood picture of Ruchir Modi with his mother\" width=\"337\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Childhood-picture-of-Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111697\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Childhood picture of Ruchir Modi with his mother<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_111682\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111682\" class=\" wp-image-111682\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi with his mother\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-mother-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi with his mother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Ruchir has a sister, Aliya Modi, who is an interior designer. Aliya is married to Brett Carlson, who belongs to California, US.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111683\" style=\"width: 364px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-sister-Aliya-Modi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111683\" class=\" wp-image-111683\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-sister-Aliya-Modi.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi with his sister, Aliya Modi\" width=\"354\" height=\"440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-sister-Aliya-Modi.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-sister-Aliya-Modi-241x300.jpg 241w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111683\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi with his sister, Aliya Modi<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He has a stepsister, Karima Sagrani, who is the daughter of Minal Modi and her first husband, Jack Sagrani. Karima is married to Gaurav Burman, director of the Dabur group.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111689\" style=\"width: 319px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-stepsister-Karima-Sagrani.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111689\" class=\" wp-image-111689\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-stepsister-Karima-Sagrani.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's stepsister, Karima Sagrani\" width=\"309\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-stepsister-Karima-Sagrani.jpg 597w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-stepsister-Karima-Sagrani-293x300.jpg 293w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-stepsister-Karima-Sagrani-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 309px) 100vw, 309px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111689\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s stepsister, Karima Sagrani<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Other_Relatives\"><\/span><strong>Other Relatives<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ruchir&#8217;s grandfather, Krishan Kumar Modi, was an Indian businessman and the President of Modi Enterprises, who passed away in 2019.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111709\" style=\"width: 374px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandfather.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111709\" class=\" wp-image-111709\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandfather.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's grandfather\" width=\"364\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandfather.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandfather-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandfather-768x575.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111709\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s grandfather<\/p><\/div>\n<p>His grandmother&#8217;s name is Bina Modi.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111710\" style=\"width: 380px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandmother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111710\" class=\" wp-image-111710\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandmother.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's grandmother\" width=\"370\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandmother.jpg 592w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-grandmother-222x300.jpg 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111710\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s grandmother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Ruchir&#8217;s uncle&#8217;s name is Samir Modi and his aunt&#8217;s name is Charu Bhartia.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111711\" style=\"width: 383px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-uncle-Samir-Modi.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111711\" class=\" wp-image-111711\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-uncle-Samir-Modi.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's uncle, Samir Modi\" width=\"373\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-uncle-Samir-Modi.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-uncle-Samir-Modi-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-uncle-Samir-Modi-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 373px) 100vw, 373px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111711\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s uncle, Samir Modi<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"RelationshipsAffairs\"><\/span>Relationships\/Affairs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ruchir Modi was in a relationship with Anastasia Fuks, who belongs to an eminent Russian real estate mogul family.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111690\" style=\"width: 469px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-girlfriend-Anastasia-Fuks.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111690\" class=\"wp-image-111690\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-girlfriend-Anastasia-Fuks.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi with his girlfriend Anastasia Fuks\" width=\"459\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-girlfriend-Anastasia-Fuks.jpg 795w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-girlfriend-Anastasia-Fuks-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-girlfriend-Anastasia-Fuks-768x580.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 459px) 100vw, 459px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111690\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi with his girlfriend Anastasia Fuks<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Anastasia was previously married to a Libyan, Massoud Abdelhafid, in 2016.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Intern\"><\/span><strong>Intern<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2013, Ruchir worked as an intern at <span class=\"t-14 t-normal\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">House of Commons in London under the mentorship of Keith Vaz, a Member of Parliament for Leicester East and Chairman of the Home Affairs Select Committee. In 2014, he was an intern at Freuds in London.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chief_Executive_Officer\"><\/span><strong>Chief Executive Officer<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ruchir is the CEO-founder of Modi Ventures. The company was founded by Ruchir in 2014, and it aimed at providing the most innovative technology projects to the Indian market.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"President\"><\/span><strong>President<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ruchir served as the President of the Rajasthan Cricket Association in the Alwar district from 2016 to 2020.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Director\"><\/span><strong>Director<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2016, Ruchir was appointed as a director at Modicare Ltd (K.K. Modi Group). Modicare offers products in the categories of personal care, color cosmetics &amp; skin care, home care, laundry care, agriculture, auto care, nutrition, food &amp; beverage, and health &amp; wellness. In the same year, he joined Modi Enterprises (K.K. Modi Group) as a director. On 19 March 2016, Ruchir was appointed as a director at Godfrey Phillips India Ltd, a tobacco manufacturing company headquartered in India. He joined Peyotito Restaurant as a director along with his sister Aliya Modi.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Car_Collection\"><\/span>Car Collection<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ruchir Modi owns cars like McLaren 720S, Bentley Mulsanne, Mercedes-Benz\u00a0AMG G 63, and Ferrari 488 Pista Spider.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_111692\" style=\"width: 335px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111692\" class=\" wp-image-111692\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's McLaren 720S car\" width=\"325\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car.jpg 601w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-McLaren-720S-car-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 325px) 100vw, 325px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111692\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s McLaren 720S car<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_111693\" style=\"width: 339px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-Mercedes-Benz-AMG-G-63-car.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111693\" class=\" wp-image-111693\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-Mercedes-Benz-AMG-G-63-car.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi's Mercedes-Benz\u00a0AMG G 63 car\" width=\"329\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-Mercedes-Benz-AMG-G-63-car.jpg 553w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modis-Mercedes-Benz-AMG-G-63-car-277x300.jpg 277w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111693\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi&#8217;s Mercedes-Benz\u00a0AMG G 63 car<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_111694\" style=\"width: 342px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111694\" class=\" wp-image-111694\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi with his Ferrari car\" width=\"332\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-with-his-Ferrari-car-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 332px) 100vw, 332px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111694\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi with his Ferrari car<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2016, Ruchir was appointed as Brand Head of India for Fashion TV.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Ruchir is a fitness enthusiast, and he practices yoga on a regular basis.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_111695\" style=\"width: 333px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-practising-yoga.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111695\" class=\" wp-image-111695\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-practising-yoga.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi practising yoga\" width=\"323\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-practising-yoga.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-practising-yoga-289x300.jpg 289w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 323px) 100vw, 323px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111695\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi practising yoga<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Ruchir is often spotted drinking alcohol with friends at parties and events.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_111698\" style=\"width: 317px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111698\" class=\" wp-image-111698\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol.jpg\" alt=\"Ruchir Modi holding a glass of alcohol\" width=\"307\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Ruchir-Modi-holding-a-glass-of-alcohol-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 307px) 100vw, 307px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111698\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ruchir Modi holding a glass of alcohol<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 15 July 2022, Ruchir&#8217;s father, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/lalit-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Lalit Modi<\/a>, took to social media to announce his relationship\u00a0with <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sushmita-sen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sushmita Sen<\/a>, a former Miss Universe and actress.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_111696\" style=\"width: 939px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Lalit-Modis-Instagram-post-in-which-he-announced-his-relationship-with-actress-Sushmita-Sen.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-111696\" class=\"size-full wp-image-111696\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Lalit-Modis-Instagram-post-in-which-he-announced-his-relationship-with-actress-Sushmita-Sen.jpg\" alt=\"Lalit Modi's Instagram post in which he announced his relationship with actress Sushmita Sen\" width=\"929\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Lalit-Modis-Instagram-post-in-which-he-announced-his-relationship-with-actress-Sushmita-Sen.jpg 929w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Lalit-Modis-Instagram-post-in-which-he-announced-his-relationship-with-actress-Sushmita-Sen-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Lalit-Modis-Instagram-post-in-which-he-announced-his-relationship-with-actress-Sushmita-Sen-768x370.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 929px) 100vw, 929px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-111696\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lalit Modi&#8217;s Instagram post in which he announced his relationship with actress Sushmita Sen<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In an interview, on being asked about his father&#8217;s relationship with Sushmita Sen, Ruchir said,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>I prefer to refrain from commenting on personal family affairs but would always be happy to comment in relation to business or other matters. I prefer not to comment at all, to be very honest, as we don\u2019t comment on personal matters as a family policy.&#8221; <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_111594_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_111594_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/entertainment\/hindi\/bollywood\/news\/sushmita-sen-dating-lalit-modi-son-ruchir-modi-reacts-his-life-his-decision-exclusive\/articleshow\/92898298.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times of India<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Since childhood, Ruchir had a great interest in cricket.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 15 January 2023, Lalit Modi announced on Twitter that he had made <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ruchir-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ruchir Modi<\/a>\u00a0his successor beneficiary from his family\u2019s side with immediate effect. Lalit Modi also announced that Ruchir would be the head of his branch of the family through a letter on Twitter.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">l In light of what I have gone thru, it\u2019s time to retire and move on. And groom my kids. I am handing them all. \ud83d\ude00\ud83e\udd70 <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/DihwLqJd5e\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com\/DihwLqJd5e<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Lalit Kumar Modi (@LalitKModi) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/LalitKModi\/status\/1614535091337809922?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">January 15, 2023<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_111594_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_111594_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_111594_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_111594_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_111594_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_111594_1_1');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1,<\/a> <a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_111594_1_2\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_111594_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_111594_1_2');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>2<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/ruchirmodi\/details\/experience\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Ruchir L Modi &#8211; LinkedIn<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_111594_1_3\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>3<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/entertainment\/hindi\/bollywood\/news\/sushmita-sen-dating-lalit-modi-son-ruchir-modi-reacts-his-life-his-decision-exclusive\/articleshow\/92898298.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times of India<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ruchir Modi is an Indian businessman. He is known for being the son of Lalit Modi, an Indian entrepreneur and cricket administrator. Wiki\/Biography Ruchir Kumar Modi Ruchir L Modi &#8211; LinkedIn was born on Friday, 9 September 1994 (age 28 years; as of 2022) in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. His zodiac sign is Virgo. Ruchir attended the American School of Bombay (1997-2010) and the American School in London (2010-2012). He holds a bachelor&#8217;s degree in global business management from Regent&#8217;s University, London. Ruchir L Modi &#8211; LinkedIn Physical Appearance Height (approx.): 5&#8242; 7&#8243; Weight (approx.): 65 kg Hair Colour: Black Eye <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":57,"featured_media":111676,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/111594"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/57"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=111594"}],"version-history":[{"count":14,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/111594\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":140888,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/111594\/revisions\/140888"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/111676"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=111594"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=111594"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=111594"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}